channel.title: Autospawn.cfg
channel.description:
Im confused. I am trying to add a Npc from scratch, wich is a man and i need to know what these mean
[code]Height RangeX1-RangeY1-RangeX2-RangeY2-WalkType[/code] What do i put for those, or where do i find out what to put. I tried and it compiled fine and when i ran my server, it said a bunch of stuff, and when i logged on it was just grey.

item.title: Autospawn.cfg
item.dc:creator: @Miss_Doctor Miss_Doctor
item.description:
@Miss_Doctor wrote:

Height, kinda self explanatory… for the ranges, those are just the area you want the npcs to walk to/around. If you want him still, put 0. Walktype. 1 for npc…attack disabled, use for a shop or an npc…just…there, 2 for monster…attack enabled
